alent of our workforce we believe textron’s success is born from the contributions of each person and we seek diverse individuals who bring rich experience skill talent and perspective to our team  we will continue to pioneer the future of our industries through the power of our brands our values our employees and our leadership above all else we’ll build upon our history of success by understanding our customers and delivering exciting new products that go beyond the expected global reach with approximately  employees and a worldwide presence textron provides integrated products solutions and services to customers around the world company history since  textron inc has evolved from a small industrial venture into a global network of businesses producing advanced aviation defense and industrial products frequently asked questions do you have a question about textrons businesses its history or job opportunities view the most frequently asked questions about the company   our company  textron current pricenyse txt homeaboutour company our company aboutour businesses our leadership our companycompany history global reach faqs our commitment our locations newsnews releases email alerts media resources media contacts photo  logo request investorsstock information events  information financial reports corporate governance investor resources careershear from our employees life at textron students  recent graduates experienced professionals manufacturing  operations military veterans find a career contact us a global network of businesses textron inc nyse txt is one of the world’s best known multiindustry companies recognized for its powerful brands such as bell helicopter cessna beechcraft ezgo jacobsen and many more the company leverages its global network of aircraft defense industrial and finance businesses to provide customers with innovative products and services  what began as a small new england business in  has grown into a  billion company with a worldwide presenc